text: Kingston College may refer to: *Kingston College (Queensland), in Logan City, Australia *Kingston College (British Columbia), Canada *Kingston College (England), United Kingdom *Kingston College (Jamaica), Jamaica *Kingston College (Chile), Concepción, Chile * Kingston College of Art, a former name of Kingston School of Art * Kingston College of Science, India ==See also== *Kingston Bible College, an Independent Fundamental Baptist College in Kingston, Nova Scotia, Canada
title: Kingston College
